*** Test Cases ***
Regiszter
    Open Browser    http://localhost:5173/    chrome
    Maximize Browser Window
    Sleep    5
    Execute JavaScript    document.querySelector('button.text-gray-700').click()
    Sleep    2
    Input Text    id=register-name    Gergely
    Input Text    id=register-email    gergely@example.com
    Input Text    id=register-password    Csenki12
    Input Text    id=register-password-confirm    Csenki12
    Click Element    xpath=//button[contains(@class,"bg-[#4A7434]") and contains(., "Regisztráció")]
    Sleep    5
    Close Browser

bejelentkezes
